{"type":null,"faqId":10962,"title":"荣耀3C （H30-T10&H30-U10）   设置飞行模式","answer":"<p>\n\t<b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">注意</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">：在飞行模式下，无线网络不可用。</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:-12.75pt;margin-left:63.8pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:7pt;\"> </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">方法一：在主屏幕，点击<b>设置</b></span><span> &gt; </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">更多</span><span>…</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，勾选<b>飞行模式</b>，打开飞行模式；取消勾选即可关闭飞行模式。</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:-21pt;margin-left:72.05pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:7pt;\">&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">方法二：长按电源键</span><span>-&gt;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">选择<b>飞行模式。</b></span><b><span></span></b> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:-21pt;margin-left:72.05pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><b><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=32012\" /><br />\n</b></span>\n</p>","faqTypeId":143,"faqType":"系统功能与设置","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"1723","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-System-Settings","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1397791314000,"seriesProductName":"H30-T10,H30-U10","visitedTimes":74,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"荣耀3C （H30-T10&H30-U10）","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}